      "content": "but there is no \"starting anew.\" how can you start over when the foundation itself was a fraud? every piece of me was tied to that work. it wasn't just a job, it was my whole purpose. now that it's gone, there's just this empty, hollow space where a person used to be. it's like the lights just went out and there's no reason to keep pretending they're still on.",
